    "en": {
      "title": "He asks the President to conduct an investigation on him",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Former Minister Nimal Siripala de Silva asked President Ranil Wickramasinghe today (21st) to conduct a speedy investigation into the allegations against him.",
        "The former minister also stated that he resigned from the ministerial post to allow an independent investigation when he was accused of trying to take bribe from a Japanese company.",
        "At that time, the former minister said that I want to clear my name rather than getting a ministry."
      ],
